<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<title>生命练习生的博客 </title>
		<meta name="keywords" content="博客，记录，写作，练习" />
		<meta name="description" content="记录点滴学习历程的博客札记" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/reset.css" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/user.css" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/font-awesome.min.css" />
		<script type="text/javascript" src="/js/jquery.min.js" ></script>
	</head>
	<body>
	<header class="header">
			<div class="table">
			<div class="container">
				<a href="#blog">
					<img src="<% if (user.imgurl) { -%>
						<%=user.imgurl %>
					<% } else { -%>
						/avatar/default.jpg
					<% } -%>" alt="我的头像" class="user-avatar"/>
				</a>
				<h1>
					<a href="#blog" title="前往“生命练习生”的主页" class="user-name">生命练习生</a>
				</h1>
				<p class="user-motto"><%=user.motto%></p>
				<hr class="divider"/>
				<p class="user-description">
					<%=user.desc%>
					<!-- Hi, 我正在努力成为一枚工程师，好奇新鲜事物，喜欢探索未知。<br />
					练习唯慢不破，喜汇编，理系统，求创新，其中苦楚谁能诉，一朝练习一朝生。 -->
				</p>
				<div class="user-social">
					<a href="https://github.com/shushu2013" target="_blank" class="user-link">
						<i class="fa fa-github fa-2x" aria-hidden="true"></i>
					</a>
					<a href="#blog" class="user-link" >
						<i class="fa fa-book fa-2x" aria-hidden="true"></i>
					</a>
					<a href="/u/<%=title%>/about" class="user-link" >
						<i class="fa fa-user fa-2x" aria-hidden="true"></i>
					</a>
					<% if (user) { %>
						<a href="/u/<%= user.name%>/setting" class="user-link" >
							<i class="fa fa-cog fa-2x" aria-hidden="true"></i>
						</a>
					<% } %>
				</div>
			</div>
			</div>
		</header>